      "body": {
        "type": "TextualBody",
        "value": "When going to find the mirror-faced person, it is her shadow attempting to make contact that we see. Yes, we are prompted to think of this as the real person, so the question becomes the difference in its intention as an experimental film technique, yet also a very intentional artistic meaning to what the character is feeling.",
